
EXECUTION
---------
codex "prompt"      - interactive session
codex exec "prompt" - one-shot batch

APPROVALS
---------
default       - adaptive prompts
--yes         - auto-approve prompts
--full-auto   - minimal prompting
-a never      - always ask

SANDBOX
-------
default               - workspace-write
-s read-only          - no file writes
-s workspace-write    - repo writes
-s danger-full-access - full access

<BREAK>

SLASH COMMANDS
--------------
/status     - session config
/diff       - show git diff
/review     - review working tree
/compact    - summarize context
/init       - scaffold AGENTS.md
/model      - switch active model
/approvals  - change approval mode

GUIDANCE FILES
--------------
~/.codex/AGENTS.md     - global rules (see codexagentshelp)
repo/AGENTS.md         - project rules
~/.codex/prompts/*.md  - custom commands
~/.codex/skills/       - (see codexskillhelp)

